divs: Sighting Details On my way to work, I work graveyard shift. Walking out to my car from my appartment, and looked up in the sky then I notice; Bright Orange Sqaure Lights coming from the north, and heading west. The object in a formation of Square, as soon it turn west it disappeared really fast. Omaha, Nebraska (Millard,Nebraska)
